District Taolagnaro, Commune Taolagnaro, localité M15, site Mandena.
Mandena forest M13. Humid littoral forest, medium level of degradation with reasonable canopy. Canopy C.5m to 8m with C.10 to 15m emergents. Stabilized (Karimbolian), dunes.
Prov: Toliara. Dist: Taolanaro. Station forestiere de Mandena.
